cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL 

The paper deals with image retrieval using deep learning techniques, specifically Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves learning pairwise image similarity, which falls under the category of metric learning, making cs.MM (Multimedia) another likely category. The paper also involves information retrieval, which falls under the category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The paper also involves optimization techniques, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves natural language processing techniques, which falls under the category of cs.CL (Computation and Language).
